{"tid":160703,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"初戀，分手了。","createTime":"2017-03-18T03:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T03:14:04.000Z","uid":22059,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f36c463f137fd7355afe6b0efdf33146694dfc1","tid":160703,"uid":22059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:22:06.000Z","msg":"曾經有多少次以後大家可以一直走到生命終結<br />\n只可惜自己不懂得愛人，一直讓你受苦<br />\n因此，即使你最後對我沒感覺，也是正常的吧<br />\n<br />\n最近我挺好的<br />\n學習把所有事情都看輕了<br />\n只是偶爾晚上想起你吧<br />\n只是拿著手機偷窺你的時間多了吧<br />\n其他都還好的<br />\n<br />\n你好嗎?<br />\n會想起我嗎? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243cc67b9e2a9f7e9ca31a89b901681e49673e92","tid":160703,"uid":12514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:27:38.000Z","msg":"佢連偷窺既機會都唔比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013d0ff8936e721db4278a5397aac530899149bd","tid":160703,"uid":38934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:29:34.000Z","msg":"冇諗起過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2527aaadaa3b8f591f85f07c845fd027954fea7","tid":160703,"uid":72769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:35:32.000Z","msg":"佢提出？因為感情淡左？"},{"pid":"bedea90402b1fe60276c5c852b94a4c0349e7075","tid":160703,"uid":29445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:37:07.000Z","msg":"可以點放低<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb284a6dc12f3c69585de616d6984cdafcfb307","tid":160703,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:53:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adce53c474ce7178b7db1eb3c71a1176203aa8a","tid":160703,"uid":22059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T04:02:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢提出？因為感情淡左？</blockquote><br />\n係.............<br />\n我係咪點改都無用....<br />\n<br />\n不過唔係佢